room_title: Escape room "Night Terror" by Get Out Southaven in Memphis
room_description: You come to it abruptly. Cold stone walls of an abandoned basement surround you. The floor is splattered with blood... You can't remember how you got here, or, more importantly, who brought you here and why. The door is locked, but you hear a man's voice outside. You tell yourself you have to be dreaming, but will you wake up before he returns?
